The town has turned into that nightmarish world.[p]
It's as if the danger in this town increases with every second.[p]
In order to find Lisa, I turn on the flashlight on my chest and begin to run at full speed.[p]
I left the antique shop with the intention of reuniting with Lisa, but I discover that all the roads leading to the hospital are blocked.[p]
With no other choice, I enter the shopping mall "Town Center" in the shopping district.[p]


