Inside, everything has naturally changed to the otherworld as well.[p]
I can hear the groans of monsters in the vicinity, and it would not be surprising if they attacked at any moment. [p]
The floor has changed to metal grating, and this building looks as if it has been left in ruins for several hundred years.[p]
Large monitors have been placed in the hall at the entrance to greet shoppers. [p]
After wandering around the first floor and finding nothing interesting, [p]
I begin heading up the powered down escalator. [p]
And at that moment...[p]


[tb_hide_message_window  ]
