Suddenly, light overflows from out of the monitors in the hall.[p]
A bound Cheryl is displayed on the screens.[p]
"Daddy...Help me!"[p]
"Cheryl!"[p]
I turn around and run back down the escalator toward the first floor hall. [p]
The image of Cheryl on the monitors then begins to get more and more fuzzy, [p]
until it dissolves into video static on the picture tube.[p]
And then, in place of Cheryl, an eerie crest is displayed.[p]
It...[p]
It looked a lot like "that" which I saw in the courtyard of the elementary school.[p]
I pound on the monitors.[p]
I pound with all my strength, as if I believed that Cheryl is trapped inside the picture tube. [p]
However, Cheryl's image did not appear again.[p]


